did.unittitle: University of Kentucky Athletic Coaches and Teams Photographs and Documents
did.abstract: The University of Kentucky Athletic Coaches and Teams Photographs and Documents (dated 1898-2019, undated; 6.09 cubic feet and 4.05 Gigabytes; 10 document boxes, 3 flat boxes, and 1265 digital files) comprise photographs and documents documenting University of Kentucky sports teams and coaches.

accessrestrict.head: Conditions Governing Access
accessrestrict.p: Collection is open to researchers by appointment

arrangement.head: Arrangement
arrangement.p: Collection is arranged into three series, Coaches, Teams, and Facilities. Within each Series, organized by name of coach, sport, or facility, and within sport, by season. Boxes are not in consecutive order.

prefercite.head: Preferred Citation
prefercite.p: 2019ua034 : [identification of item], University of Kentucky Athletic Coaches and Teams photographs and documents, 1898-2019, undated, University of Kentucky Libraries Special Collections Research Center.

scopecontent.head: Scope and Contents
scopecontent.p: The University of Kentucky Athletic Coaches and Teams photographs (dated 1898-2019, undated; 6.09 cubic feet and 4.05 Gigabytes; 10 document boxes, 3 flat boxes, and 1265 digital files) comprise photographs and a few documents documenting University of Kentucky sports teams and coaches. Sports represented include men's and women's basketball, football, baseball, golf, softball, soccer, and volleyball.

userestrict.head: Conditions Governing Use
userestrict.p: Property rights reside with the University of Kentucky. The University of Kentucky holds the copyright for materials created in the course of business by University of Kentucky employees. Copyright for all other materials has not been assigned to the University of Kentucky. For information about permission to reproduce or publish, please contact the Special Collections Research Center.
